Knowing the terror of the Lord, we persuade men.

48:19.636 --> 48:29.751
This is God's way, then, of securing the final perseverance and the ultimate glorification of His people very well, hurriedly and inadequately.

48:30.152 --> 48:36.882
We have tried to look at this problem that arises in the minds of men and women as they read

48:37.154 --> 48:43.543
There's all important statement in the 11th chapter of the Epistle to the Romans, verses 18 to 22.

48:44.084 --> 48:49.913
God willing, we shall go on to our general application of this teaching next Friday evening.

48:51.675 --> 48:59.607
O Lord, our God, we do indeed come to thee again, and we thank thee more than ever, that we are what we are by thy grace.

49:00.569 --> 49:06.898
And know that what we ever shall be shall be by thy grace, that our hope of glory

49:07.074 --> 49:21.969
lies only in this, that we belong to this election of grace, that we have been called out of darkness into thy marvelous light, that thou hast set thy heart upon us.

49:22.870 --> 49:24.572
Lord, we do not understand it.

49:25.152 --> 49:27.715
We think that we don't even desire to understand it.

49:28.255 --> 49:29.757
We are a joy in it.

49:29.777 --> 49:33.120
We know that it is the only explanation of us.

49:33.140 --> 49:34.802
We know it is our only hope.

49:35.298 --> 49:36.359
We thank thee for it.

49:36.419 --> 49:41.446
We bless and praise thy great and holy name because of it.

49:41.466 --> 50:03.314
O Lord, we pray thee to write this truth so deeply upon our minds and our hearts that we shall never be guilty of any tendency to burst either in ourselves or to boast against anybody else, forever taking heed and in a spirit of reverence and godly fear.

50:04.066 --> 50:22.068
in fear and trembling, we may work out our own salvation, knowing that it is thou who does work in us, both will and to do, and entirely, because of thy known good pleasure.

50:22.909 --> 50:30.258
O God, receive our unworthy praise and worship and admiration, and now

50:30.402 --> 50:39.558
May the grace of the Lord Jesus Christ and the love of God, and the fellowship in the communion of the Holy Spirit abide and continue with us.

50:40.159 --> 50:53.863
Now this night, throughout the remainder of this hour, short and certain earthly life and pilgrimage, and until we arrive in the glory of our lusty.

50:55.205 --> 50:55.666
Amen.

